data.description: Welcome to this must see 3 bedroom 2.5 bath Lakeview 2 story Carriage Home that lives like a Single Family home with lots of upgrades, plenty of space, and storage. The first floor features an open concept including a full kitchen with plenty of cabinets, granite counter top, stainless steal appliances, breakfast bar, pantry and access to the attached garage so you can go from your air conditioned home to you car and stay dry when carrying your groceries into your kitchen. Theres also a powder room, dinning area, and living room with sliders out to the nice sized screened in with awning Lanai where you can bbq and eat while admiring the breathtaking Lakeviews and natural landscaping. Upstairs you have a primary bedroom suite with updated full bathing and walk in closet. Down the hall you have another full bath, two bedrooms, washer+dryer so no need to carry laundry baskets up and down steps. This beautiful gated community of Stratford Place with low HOAs offers two pools & 2 spa/hot tub, clubhouse, with many other amenities in a great location close to shopping, schools, restaurants, I-75, and just 10 mins away from the beach!
